      "writtenOn": "2020-08-14T02:48:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "How would this account for steps sharing information? For example: one step queries Datastore and does some sort of validation/ manipulation, and wants to send the result of that to the next step? Would that be an antipattern?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 114,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 114,
        "endChar": 13
      },
      "revId": "6c25df5c385468967569dce9e4a0be2c04979e30",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
